article_id:2493,category_name:News,title_name:Gala Dragalia Is Coming Soon!,image_path:,message:<div>Gala Dragalia starts on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1632722400"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>■What Are Gala Dragalia and Gala Dragalia Remix?</div><div>The initial appearance rate for 5★ adventurers and dragons will be boosted to 6%, which is up from the standard 4%! If you get a 5★ summon or 5★ featured summon, the appearance rate will return to the initial 6%.</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Any Gala adventurer or dragon added in past Gala Dragalia summon showcases may appear in this summon showcase. For information about which adventurers and dragons may appear, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Appearance Rates and check the Appearance Rates section.</span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);"><br></span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Please note that only the following adventurers and dragons are featured in this summon showcase.</span></div><div><br></div><div>▼Featured adventurers from past Gala Dragalia summon showcases:</div><div>5★ Gala Notte (wind/dagger)</div><div>5★ Gala Mascula (water/blade)</div><div>5★ Gala Chelle (shadow/rapid-fire manacaster)</div><div><br></div><div>▼Featured dragons from past Gala Dragalia summon showcases:</div><div>5★ Gala Reborn Jeanne (light)</div><div>5★ Gala Reborn Agni (flame)</div><div>5★ Gala Reborn Poseidon (water)</div><div>5★ Gala Reborn Zephyr (wind)</div><div>5★ Gala Reborn Nidhogg (shadow)</div><div><br></div><div>Gala Dragalia event duration:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1632722400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1632981599"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at some of the featured adventurers and dragons below.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurers:</div><div>
